PrecisAcceptance from the Province of QUEBEC, of the transfer for the use of a beach and deep water lot (85,344.1 m²) in the Registry Division of RIMOUSKI, in the Province of Quebec, for use as a site to maintain wharves, retaining walls, a breakwater and other improvements necessary for the operation of the port at Rimouski.

precis:
Acceptance from the Province of QUEBEC, of the transfer for the use of a
beach and deep water lot (85,344.1 m²) in the Registry Division of
RIMOUSKI, in the Province of Quebec, for use as a site to maintain wharves,
